        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "Chapter seventeen",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "He continued,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "\"I do refuse it,\" I replied; \"and no torture shall ever extort a consent from me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "I am malicious because I am miserable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "This passion is detrimental to me, for you do not reflect that YOU are the cause of its excess.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "\"You swear,\" I said, \"to be harmless; but have you not already shown a degree of malice that should reasonably make me distrust you?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "His power and threats were not omitted in my calculations; a creature who could exist in the ice caves of the glaciers and hide himself from pursuit among the ridges of inaccessible precipices was a being possessing faculties it would be vain to cope with.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-17_363_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/17/363/17_363_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-17",
        "content": "I felt as if I were placed under a ban-as if I had no right to claim their sympathies-as if never more might I enjoy companionship with them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
]